(392, 84, 'adoria_values_section', 'a:7:{i:0;a:4:{s:17:"adoria_value_text";s:215:"<p class="col_text">Experience and expertise go hand in hand. Each Adoriasoft employee has gained an outright expertise in their area of knowledge and responsibility. We keep on learning, growing and evolving.</p>\r\n";s:17:"adoria_value_icon";a:5:{s:3:"url";s:77:"http://adoriasoft.dev.adoriasoft.org/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/expertise.svg";s:2:"id";s:2:"95";s:6:"height";s:0:"";s:5:"width";s:0:"";s:9:"thumbnail";s:73:"http://adoriasoft.dev.adoriasoft.org/wp-includes/images/media/default.png";}s:18:"adoria_value_title";s:10:"Experience";s:11:"ll-row-sort";s:0:"";}i:1;a:4:{s:17:"adoria_value_text";s:301:"We build relations based on reliability, personal responsibility and trust. Maintaining good reputation means a lot to any socially responsible company. A flawless reputation of Adoriasoft is not a prime goal, but simply a result of our day-to-day attitude towards all people impacted by our business.";s:17:"adoria_value_icon";a:5:{s:3:"url";s:73:"http://adoriasoft.dev.adoriasoft.org/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/trust.svg";s:2:"id";s:3:"102";s:6:"height";s:0:"";s:5:"width";s:0:"";s:9:"thumbnail";s:73:"http://adoriasoft.dev.adoriasoft.org/wp-includes/images/media/default.png";}s:18:"adoria_value_title";s:5:"Trust";s:11:"ll-row-sort";s:0:"";}i:2;a:4:{s:17:"adoria_value_text";s:448:"We keep things simple, fast and streamlined. In order to deliver what is required fast we remain connected to our clients through effective communication in the course of the whole project and beyond. To ensure that maximum value is delivered to a client just in time Adoriasoft utilizes agile development approach. This means we work together with clients and encourage them to suggest any changes for implementation during each project iteration.";s:17:"adoria_value_icon";a:5:{s:3:"url";s:75:"http://adoriasoft.dev.adoriasoft.org/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/agility.svg";s:2:"id";s:2:"96";s:6:"height";s:0:"";s:5:"width";s:0:"";s:9:"thumbnail";s:73:"http://adoriasoft.dev.adoriasoft.org/wp-includes/images/media/default.png";}s:18:"adoria_value_title";s:7:"Agility";s:11:"ll-row-sort";s:0:"";}i:3;a:4:{s:17:"adoria_value_text";s:266:"Our clients trust us, because honesty and openness are at our core. Everyone at Adoriasoft understands that relying on professionalism of others is quite a risky venture. That\'s why long ago we\'ve chosen to pursue the path of exemplary professionalism and integrity.";s:17:"adoria_value_icon";a:5:{s:3:"url";s:77:"http://adoriasoft.dev.adoriasoft.org/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/integrity.svg";s:2:"id";s:2:"99";s:6:"height";s:0:"";s:5:"width";s:0:"";s:9:"thumbnail";s:73:"http://adoriasoft.dev.adoriasoft.org/wp-includes/images/media/default.png";}s:18:"adoria_value_title";s:9:"Integrity";s:11:"ll-row-sort";s:0:"";}i:4;a:4:{s:17:"adoria_value_text";s:363:"With the majority of Adoriasoft developers holding a PhD in Computer Science, as well as being proficient in English, it\'s no wonder that most our clients have been working with us for many years. Constantly mastering new technology-oriented skills our talented team members continue their self development and self actualization. We don\'t stop and we won\'t stop.";s:17:"adoria_value_icon";a:5:{s:3:"url";s:74:"http://adoriasoft.dev.adoriasoft.org/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/talent.svg";s:2:"id";s:3:"101";s:6:"height";s:0:"";s:5:"width";s:0:"";s:9:"thumbnail";s:73:"http://adoriasoft.dev.adoriasoft.org/wp-includes/images/media/default.png";}s:18:"adoria_value_title";s:6:"Talent";s:11:"ll-row-sort";s:0:"";}i:5;a:4:{s:17:"adoria_value_text";s:399:"At Adoriasoft we are driven towards a single goal - successful implementation and delivery of the desired solution or system to clients. Our team is the leadership team of motivated, highly skilled individuals who incorporate required changes and overcome unforeseen challenges throughout the development process. From day to day, hour to hour we work on building solutions that lead you to success.";s:17:"adoria_value_icon";a:5:{s:3:"url";s:78:"http://adoriasoft.dev.adoriasoft.org/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/leadership.svg";s:2:"id";s:3:"100";s:6:"height";s:0:"";s:5:"width";s:0:"";s:9:"thumbnail";s:73:"http://adoriasoft.dev.adoriasoft.org/wp-includes/images/media/default.png";}s:18:"adoria_value_title";s:10:"Leadership";s:11:"ll-row-sort";s:0:"";}i:6;a:4:{s:17:"adoria_value_text";s:337:"Today for companies to stay in business in any industry ongoing modernization, optimization of their technical capabilities and processes are required. Adoriasoft keeps its ears pressed to the latest trends of technology world. We effectively deploy innovation in every our project, while maintaining cost-effectiveness and set timeline.";s:17:"adoria_value_icon";a:5:{s:3:"url";s:78:"http://adoriasoft.dev.adoriasoft.org/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/innovation.svg";s:2:"id";s:2:"98";s:6:"height";s:0:"";s:5:"width";s:0:"";s:9:"thumbnail";s:73:"http://adoriasoft.dev.adoriasoft.org/wp-includes/images/media/default.png";}s:18:"adoria_value_title";s:10:"Innovation";s:11:"ll-row-sort";s:0:"";}}'),
